IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SYSTEM-MATH.

DATA DIVISION.
01 A PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 B PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 C PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 5 TO A
    MOVE 10 TO B
    ADD A TO B
    DISPLAY "B AFTER ADD: " B
    MULTIPLY 4 BY A GIVING C
    DISPLAY "C AFTER MULTIPLY: " C
    SUBTRACT 1 FROM 2 GIVING A
    DISPLAY "A AFTER SUBTRACT: " A.
